{{champion:25}} {{champion:10}} 

I've probably missed a pair, but I think it would be interesting to learn more about the League's sibling pairs. I think these are some interesting veins to mine just looking and learning more about them. 

The soldier who served and the brother who serves only himself.

Not sure how deep the brothers from Noxus story would go, but it could be amusing to look at their upbringing and the differences in their lives that both led them to the league.

The angel and her fallen sister. 

Kayle and Morg are two champs with backstories, that while interesting, show their age. I think these two have a lot of room for the Riot Writers to really dive in and do something amazing and new.

The sisters of a dark, noble house; the deadly assassin and their strangely cursed, scheming sister.

We got to see Cass' curse, but I think her story immediately after her change could be something. Having to return home so vastly changed, does she feel like a freak and a failure or does she revel in her new power? And if it's truly a curse, why does it bestow power? How did her family react? Those in her highborn social circle? What do Kat (and Talon as well) think? And what happened to their father? Is one of them possibly responsible?

