As a Jinx main since her release, I pick the city of Piltover. I'd like some resolution to the Vi/Jinx sibling thing. 

Are they siblings? Are they not? Do they have siblings? If they aren't siblings, will Jinx's crazy sister or Vi's sister who resembles her be a future champ?  Also, what is the state of Piltover now that Jinx has wrecked havoc? Who is "C" is Caitlyn's lore?
